data.description: Welcome to a remarkable investment opportunity! This property is nestled on the outskirts of vibrant North San Antonio. This hidden gem holds immense potential, sprawling across a generous 2.9-acre parcel of unrestricted land, offering endless possibilities for those seeking an ideal sanctuary. As you explore this charming single-story ranch-style home with three spacious bedrooms and two full baths, envision the renovations needed to tailor it to your exact standards. Seize this unique opportunity to craft your own hill country haven - a chance you wouldn't want to miss. The absence of an HOA is an added benefit, and being situated within the esteemed COMAL Independent School District ensures exceptional educational opportunities for your family. Step outside and embrace the tranquility of mature, wooded surroundings, creating a captivating natural retreat. Positioned adjacent to Timberwood Park and conveniently near Borgfeld Rd, this location provides easy access to amenities, including the new Pieper HS, grocery stores, shopping, and more.
